// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1457 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: c8152ad3-880c-510e-ba7f-d5b44e7e331d

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:8*")
